WEBVTT

00:00.105 --> 00:04.672
A peace treaty has been ratified
with the Emperor of France.

00:04.829 --> 00:07.299
Who will now be our gallant ally.

00:07.505 --> 00:09.320
It'll come to war again.

00:09.622 --> 00:12.992
I am in love with Sonya
and I want us to be married.

00:12.993 --> 00:14.025
You had better know that

00:14.025 --> 00:16.989
I can never recognise that
intriguer as my daughter!

00:16.989 --> 00:18.989
My father made it a
condition of his consent

00:18.989 --> 00:20.928
that the marriage not
take place for a year.

00:20.929 --> 00:22.056
I'll wait.

00:22.057 --> 00:24.993
- You're so lovely.
- You mustn't say that!

00:24.993 --> 00:26.037
Why ever not?

00:27.065 --> 00:30.001
Will you tell Prince
Andrei when he comes

00:30.001 --> 00:31.985
that our engagement is at an end...

00:31.985 --> 00:33.061
and I cannot be his wife.

00:33.061 --> 00:35.073
He loves me, Sonya!

00:35.073 --> 00:38.029
I'd do anything...
I'd run away with him!

00:38.029 --> 00:40.029
You're to come with us, sir.

00:40.029 --> 00:42.005
We've been betrayed!

00:42.005 --> 00:43.053
No!

00:43.053 --> 00:45.057
I will go to him, wherever he is!

00:45.057 --> 00:47.997
He's a married man,
he has a wife in Poland!

